# No AI Co-Author Attribution

NEVER add a Co-authored-by trailer, --trailer flag, or any other form of AI attribution to git commits.

- Do NOT append `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any variant
- Do NOT add `--trailer` flags to git commit commands
- Do NOT add any AI tool or assistant as a co-author, contributor, or committer
- Commit messages must only credit human authors

This applies to ALL git operations: commits, amends, rebases, cherry-picks, and merge commits.
